#: ../new/buildtime.rst:7
msgid "Build Time"
msgstr ""

#: ../new/buildtime.rst:9
msgid ""
"In :game:`Ares` it is possible to customize all settings related to the "
"build time of objects per type."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/buildtime.rst:17
msgid ":tagdef:`[TechnoType]BuildTime.Speed=double - minutes`"
msgstr ""

#: ../new/buildtime.rst:13
msgid ""
"The time in minutes it takes to produce an object which costs 1000 "
"credits. Defaults to :tag:`[General]BuildSpeed`."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/buildtime.rst:16
msgid ""
"If set, :tag:`WallBuildSpeedCoefficient` will not be applied to "
":tag:`Wall=yes` buildings any more, because :tag:`BuildTime.Speed` is "
"taken as final value."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/buildtime.rst:21
msgid ":tagdef:`[TechnoType]BuildTime.Cost=integer - credits`"
msgstr ""

#: ../new/buildtime.rst:20
msgid ""
"If set, the build time is calculated as if this item cost this much, "
"instead of using actual :tag:`Cost`. Defaults to :tag:`Cost`."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/buildtime.rst:23
msgid ""
"If the player does not have enough power, the following settings apply. "
"They define a factor applied to the amount of power lacking and the range"
" the resulting modifier will be clamped in before being multipled with "
"the build time."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/buildtime.rst:30
msgid ":tagdef:`[TechnoType]BuildTime.LowPowerPenalty=double - multiplier`"
msgstr ""

#: ../new/buildtime.rst:29
msgid ""
"The penalty to apply to the build time in low power situations. Defaults "
"to :tag:`[General]LowPowerPenaltyModifier`."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/buildtime.rst:35
msgid ":tagdef:`[TechnoType]BuildTime.MinLowPower=double`"
msgstr ""

#: ../new/buildtime.rst:33
msgid ""
"The minimum production speed when power is low. The resulting low power "
"modifier will not be lower than this. Defaults to "
":tag:`[General]MinLowPowerProductionSpeed`."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/buildtime.rst:40
msgid ":tagdef:`[TechnoType]BuildTime.MaxLowPower=double`"
msgstr ""

#: ../new/buildtime.rst:38
msgid ""
"The maximum production speed when power is low. The resulting low power "
"modifier will not be greater than this. Defaults to "
":tag:`[General]MaxLowPowerProductionSpeed`."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/buildtime.rst:42
msgid ""
"When a player has more than one factory of the same type, the following "
"modifier also applies."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/buildtime.rst:47
msgid ":tagdef:`[TechnoType]BuildTime.MultipleFactory=double - multiplier`"
msgstr ""

#: ../new/buildtime.rst:46
msgid ""
"The factor multiplied by the build time per additional factory of the "
"same type. Defaults to :tag:`[General]MultipleFactory`."
msgstr ""

